OL,4,G2000FBoon
OL,5,     GKen and Margaret's attempts to
OL,6,     Gnail a gangster are less than
OL,7,     Gsuccessful, and Harry is
OL,8,     Gapproached by a lugubrious former
OL,9,     Gcolleague from the fire brigade
OL,10,     Gwho has 'found religion'.
OL,11,G2100FThe Man Who Made Husbands Jealous
OL,12,     GThe steamy classic from Rivals
OL,13,     Gauthor Jilly Cooper. Broke and
OL,14,     Ginfamous, Lysander Hawkley turns
OL,15,     Gtabloid notoriety into seducing
OL,16,     Gwronged wives.
OL,17,G2205FMission Killfast
OL,18,     GAn adrenalized thrill ride with a
OL,19,     Ghigh-kicking CIA agent, Vegas
OL,20,     Ggangsters, mad arms dealers,
OL,21,     Gnuclear terrorists, explosions,
OL,22,     Gand bikini-clad beauties.
